For of JsonPath 0.9.0 to enable writing to a resolved path

------------------------------------------
0.0.1                       2014-07-04
------------------------------------------
Usage :
ReadContext rc = JsonPath.parse(json);
JsonPathReplacement replacement = new JsonPathReplacement("$.telephone","+42 422 1242 1244");
rc.replace(replacement);
String substituteJSON = rc.json().toString()